Steps:-

1. making box sizing property to border-box 
"* {box-sizing: "border-box" }"
"which means the content will include the border. also, it's helful when we work with width of content"

2. setting the default font family which can be accessible by whole website
"html { font-family: "roboto"}

3. creating global css variables for colors.

    EXAMPLE = --variableName-type-hardness :  rgb(37, 34, 31)

    --color-gray-500: rgb(37, 34, 31);
    --color-gray-800: rgb(15, 15, 14);

